	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />The famicom that looks like the nes2 is the famicom av. It ouputs ntsc. You need a special power adaptor (polarity wise its reversed from what's "standard") So one of those adjustable power supplies is recommended. You have to use a snes/n64/gc av cable with it. You need a nes game to famicom adaptor....but those arent TOO expensive if you know where to look.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


